Package net.cloud.server.event.command

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Command
    A Command, which is meant to perform some action dynamically.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommandHandler
    An entrance point to the command subsystem.
    CommandPrototypes
    Contains a mapping of command names to prototype instances.
    CommandReader
    Despite the name, no this class is not a subclass of Reader.
    CommandScriptReader
    This despite its name is not a Reader, either.
    CommandService
    A CommandService is a service running on its own thread that will read commands from the provided input, parse them, have them executed via the task engine, and return the result of the command through the provided output.
    CommandServiceThread
    A runnable object which takes care of the I/O associated with reading a command string and shipping it off for handling
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CommandException
    An Exception used by the Command system.
